                     <interp inst="t18410823-2238-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18410823-cd-253" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18410823-2238-offence-1 t18410823-cd-253"></join>22nd of August</rs>, 1 pair of boots, value 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18410823-name-1356" type="victimName">
